## PR Info

- Dependents:
  - https://github.com/SeaQL/sea-orm/pull/1474

## New Features

- [x] Implemented `PartialEq` for `SimpleExpr` and on its related types

## Breaking Changes

- [x] Remaned `SeaRc` into `RcOrArc`
- [x] Added a new struct `SeaRc` which resemble the API of `SeaRC` as it used to be
```rs
let table_as: DynIden = SeaRc::new(Alias::new("char"));
// Or,
let table_as: DynIden = Alias::new("char").into_iden();

// Clone it
let cloned: DynIden = SeaRc::clone(&table_as);

// From a enum Iden
let char_id: DynIden = Character::Id.into_iden();
```
